<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 01:09:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>关于美国黑人移民的主要发现</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/20/key-findings-about-black-immigrants-in-the-us/</link><description>自2000年以来，美国黑人移民人口增加了一倍多，到2024年将达到560万，目前占黑人总人口的11.4%。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 01:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/20/key-findings-about-black-immigrants-in-the-us/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国人更喜欢拥有大房子的分散社区</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/19/majority-of-americans-prefer-spread-out-communities-with-big-houses/</link><description>55% 的美国人表示，他们更愿意居住在房屋更大、距离便利设施更远的社区，而 44% 的人则持相反观点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 01:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/19/majority-of-americans-prefer-spread-out-communities-with-big-houses/</guid></item><item><title>美国人认为什么是不道德的？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/03/19/what-do-americans-consider-immoral/</link><description>十分之九的美国人认为外遇是错误的。共和党和民主党在堕胎和同性恋的道德问题上存在巨大分歧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/03/19/what-do-americans-consider-immoral/</guid></item><item><title>美国男人和女人如何度过他们的时间？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/social-trends/feature/how-do-u-s-men-and-women-spend-their-time/</link><description>探索美国人如何按性别和年龄组分配时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 01:11:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/social-trends/feature/how-do-u-s-men-and-women-spend-their-time/</guid></item><item><title>与许多其他国家的人相比，美国人不太可能认为赌博在道德上是错误的</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/16/americans-are-less-likely-than-people-in-many-other-countries-to-see-gambling-as-morally-wrong/</link><description>在许多其他接受调查的国家，大约一半或更多的成年人认为赌博是不道德的。其中印度尼西亚为 89%，印度为 83%，意大利为 71%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/16/americans-are-less-likely-than-people-in-many-other-countries-to-see-gambling-as-morally-wrong/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普上任第一年联邦劳动力减少10%</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/13/federal-workforce-shrank-10-in-trumps-first-year-back-in-office/</link><description>2025 年，联邦劳动力将减少 10.3%，失去近 238,000 名工人。在主要机构中，教育部和美国国际开发署的削减幅度最大。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 01:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/13/federal-workforce-shrank-10-in-trumps-first-year-back-in-office/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国人仍然认为堕胎在所有或大多数情况下都应该合法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/03/12/majority-of-americans-continue-to-say-abortion-should-be-legal-in-all-or-most-cases/</link><description>60% 的大多数美国成年人表示，在所有或大多数情况下堕胎应该是合法的。这一比例较过去几年略有下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 01:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/03/12/majority-of-americans-continue-to-say-abortion-should-be-legal-in-all-or-most-cases/</guid></item><item><title>公众对堕胎的看法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/fact-sheet/public-opinion-on-abortion/</link><description>堕胎在美国长期以来一直是一个有争议的问题，也是美国人在党派、意识形态和宗教方面产生严重分歧的一个问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Jun 2025 00:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/fact-sheet/public-opinion-on-abortion/</guid></item><item><title>关于美国人如何看待人工智能的主要发现</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/key-findings-about-how-americans-view-artificial-intelligence/</link><description>根据皮尤研究中心五年来的调查，以下是关于美国人如何使用和看待人工智能，以及他们在哪里看到前景和风险的 13 项调查结果。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/key-findings-about-how-americans-view-artificial-intelligence/</guid></item><item><title>美国人如何看待数据中心对从环境​​到就业等关键领域的影响</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/how-americans-view-data-centers-impact-in-key-areas-from-the-environment-to-jobs/</link><description>表示数据中心对环境、家庭能源成本和附近人们的生活质量产生负面影响的美国人多于表示产生积极影响的美国人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/how-americans-view-data-centers-impact-in-key-areas-from-the-environment-to-jobs/</guid></item></channel></rss>